{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "padelito-elo-flow-test",
    "name": "Padelito - ELO Flow Test",
    "description": "Scénario complet : 4 joueurs (P1+P2 vs P3+P4), match ranked doubles, invitations, score 2-1, 4 confirmations, vérification ELO.\n\nLe script tourne en séquence dans le **Collection Runner** (ou Newman). Tous les tokens et IDs sont auto-stockés via les scripts Tests.\n\n**ELO attendu (joueurs à 1500, 0 match joué, K=40, sets 2-1, multiplicateur 1.0)**\n- Team A (P1+P2) → +20 pts → 1520\n- Team B (P3+P4) → -20 pts → 1480",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8001" },
    { "key": "token_p1",         "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_p2",         "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_p3",         "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_p4",         "value": "" },
    { "key": "player_id_p1",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "player_id_p2",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "player_id_p3",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "player_id_p4",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "match_id",         "value": "" },
    { "key": "inv_id_p2",        "value": "" },
    { "key": "inv_id_p3",        "value": "" },
    { "key": "inv_id_p4",        "value": "" },
    { "key": "_ts",              "value": "" }
  ],
